{"tid":27700,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主人成日嘔","createTime":"2016-12-07T13:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T17:43:28.000Z","uid":37393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1208632eeb3e9de43d3f98faf485b2e99570a564","tid":27700,"uid":37393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"家中有兩隻主人, 明明無轉過糧,但係呢排成日都嘔,有時嘔水 有時嘔返原粒未爛既乾糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外就係一開餐既時候成日比細主人搶住食哂,食完自己果D又食埋人地果D,大主人又次次都等細主人食完哂啦,佢先開始食,好禮讓好乖,但依家好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下巴打可以有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e61e33c72c40289e79feb6bc50abc3fe22b8ee1","tid":27700,"uid":38654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"有無餵佢食貓草/吐毛膏?"},{"pid":"44f29cfa65c35b621de7e93b5a07954447090f4f","tid":27700,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"我兩隻都係咁<br />\n有時食得太急<br />\n有時隻糧敏感<br />\n有時真係有毛或者污糟野想嘔出黎"},{"pid":"aa269466905dd56874a704eb7f97ff95bda8b825","tid":27700,"uid":37393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無餵佢食貓草/吐毛膏?</blockquote><br />\n未餵啊,巴打有無邊隻好推介,係要貓草同吐毛膏 雙管齊下定係食一款就夠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea8875ca3792803a06d60745538c9b4a5a26b93","tid":27700,"uid":37393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我兩隻都係咁<br />\n<br />\n有時食得太急<br />\n<br />\n有時隻糧敏感<br />\n<br />\n有時真係有毛或者污糟野想嘔出黎</blockquote><br />\n但係嘔得都好密下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中一隻貓讓哂D野食比第二隻可以點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經分兩個兜都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ebee7bd77a698d3d7ecd3445c4fccf10672319","tid":27700,"uid":38654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無餵佢食貓草/吐毛膏?</blockquote><br />\n未餵啊,巴打有無邊隻好推介,係要貓草同吐毛膏 雙管齊下定係食一款就夠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓草會好啲<br />\n可能有太多毛積住<br />\n加上轉天氣<br />\n我果兩隻都有嘔<br />\n食得太急就會<br />\n<br />\n分兩個兜再分兩個地方擺<br />\n等佢地習慣有自己地盤食<br />\n唔好放長糧<br />\n會變濕同變腍<br />\n都會嘔"},{"pid":"2bd5f6a47ed6dc6090f4114e0388a337c3d49cd7","tid":27700,"uid":31988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無餵佢食貓草/吐毛膏?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未餵啊,巴打有無邊隻好推介,係要貓草同吐毛膏 雙管齊下定係食一款就夠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貓草會好啲<br />\n<br />\n可能有太多毛積住<br />\n<br />\n加上轉天氣<br />\n<br />\n我果兩隻都有嘔<br />\n<br />\n食得太急就會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分兩個兜再分兩個地方擺<br />\n<br />\n等佢地習慣有自己地盤食<br />\n<br />\n唔好放長糧<br />\n<br />\n會變濕同變腍<br />\n<br />\n都會嘔</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4d8c3fc53b3be70abcfff58e89a14a1287b58f4b","tid":27700,"uid":31988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家中有兩隻主人, 明明無轉過糧,但係呢排成日都嘔,有時嘔水 有時嘔返原粒未爛既乾糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係一開餐既時候成日比細主人搶住食哂,食完自己果D又食埋人地果D,大主人又次次都等細主人食完哂啦,佢先開始食,好禮讓好乖,但依家好瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下巴打可以有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有機會係食得太急 我主人都會咁"},{"pid":"68b3c66d955b1ea3bdaffe36e25b8684ea79575e","tid":27700,"uid":50108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無餵佢食貓草/吐毛膏?</blockquote><br />\n未餵啊,巴打有無邊隻好推介,係要貓草同吐毛膏 雙管齊下定係食一款就夠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己種啦 生得勁快 又有益點 我隻貓超級鐘意食"}]}